{"tid":1745790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住九龍灣手足，九龍灣連儂牆毁滅了","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T02:05:39.000Z","uid":205617,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"82541d1f78ab8540b3809a5991ee82f6ead389da","tid":1745790,"uid":205617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"小弟對大家唔住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係一個一人發夢人士<br />\n冇隊友，由6月開始到以家<br />\n有活動就出去，冇活動就做文宣<br />\n間唔中都綠色線各個連儂牆睇吓有冇事<br />\n琴日小弟病咗，冇去睇一睇<br />\n今日好翻啲就落去睇吓<br />\n見到面目全非，好心痛<br />\n此post希望大家用不推文<br />\n當比我發洩下，就算<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"9d7e2e80534b2468a515a23ba5094c9bb4c6fca1","tid":1745790,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518da306a44bd790c2f6a2546b51828b5434f93d","tid":1745790,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:41:15.000Z","msg":"再起囉 預咗比人撕"},{"pid":"ba8e051fec886ba6c03e8ddd849cf4310a5913aa","tid":1745790,"uid":285716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:41:52.000Z","msg":"一齊再整過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e62d8bdf415f6b87a4498e4b5076ff962e25710","tid":1745790,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"大把同路人一齊貼返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cd4d69bdddf04b57606ab296d631d727333aab","tid":1745790,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"提我地係時候更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829ced7a97e6a